  "title": "(Immediate Hiring)  Picker & Packer - West / Transport Provided/ Training Provided [R22107578]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Summary:</strong></p><ul><li>Work life balance </li><li>Company transport provided </li><li>Training will be provided</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Pick, pack, and label goods accurately according to orders and packing lists.</li><li>Perform basic quality checks to ensure items are in good condition before packing.</li><li>Assist with loading, unloading, and handling of goods, including manual lifting when required.</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and organization of the warehouse and packing area.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Training provided, all are welcome to apply.</li></ul><p><br /><br /></p><p>To Apply, kindly click on the <strong>\"APPLY NOW\"</strong> button</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><strong>Staffking Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Jasmine Wong (R22107578)</strong></p>",
